            <h1>Myths and misconceptions</h1>
            <div class="misconceptions" id="m0"><p><h3>Why do people not vaccinate their children?</h3></br>There are several reasons why some parents have decided not to vaccinate their children. The greatest reason is safety concerns, most of which are based on information the parents have received from the media or acquaintances. Religious and philosophical reasons are generally linked to the core beliefs of the parents. One last possible reason is that the parents have limited access to vaccinations due to living in below average conditions.

